<p>In addition to his acting credits Bono has contributed music to films, as part of U2 and as part of other collaborations. In <i>Across the Universe</i> he sang <a href="The_Beatles" title="The Beatles">The Beatles</a> songs "<a href="I_Am_the_Walrus" title="I Am the Walrus">I Am the Walrus</a>" and "<a href="Lucy_in_the_Sky_with_Diamonds" title="Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds">Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds</a>".</p>
